		   <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform" ><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=494"><span id=Scholar>Braun</span></a><b><span id=Scholar><br>Scholar</span></b><br><img src=/shared/user_star_ico.gif height=9 width=9><br>56 posts
		   <br><nobr><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good [3.75]</nobr><br><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=Braun&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%"><p>Dex only helps procs and crits. It does not increase your chances to hit.<br><br>AGI only increases your AC (and supposedly helps you take less damage when hit, but this has yet o be proven to me) It does not increase your chances to hit.<br><br>Advances in your weapon skills directly affect your ATK rating.<br><br>STR directly affects your carrying capacity and raises your ATK.&nbsp;&nbsp;Also increases your max damage slightly.<br><br>ATK is the key here. The higher your ATK rating, the more likely your going to hit.<br><br>Easy way to test this: Create a new warrior. Go out and bash things to level 10, maxing out skills.  Get yourself killed a lot, back down to level 5 or so.  Your ATK rating doesn't go down and you lose no skills, they just stop advancing.<br>So now you have a level 5 with level 10 skills.  Go swing at some even cons and you'll notice just how much easier you can hit the mob.<br><br>Strange way to test? This happend to one of my charactors.  I was bound at the FP gates (guards were glowering).  Over the course of the time I went from level 4 to 10, I'd messed up my faction with FP militia pretty good.  One night I fall asleep at the Nro tunnel and was trained sometime in the middle of the night.  Woke up level 5 being beat to death again at my bind point in NFp.  Thats when I tested this theory for real =).</p><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br>Braun - 59ish Ogre Warrior<br>Torvonnilous</td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="100%"><tr><td id=fs8></td><td align=ri